<span id="freeTextContainer9050264561852057049">One of the greatest epics of human civilisation, and a masterpiece of myth and legend. <br/><br/>As a result of its almost absurd scope and sheer length, I must admit to have merely skimmed this work (twice), but I aim to fully read it one day.<br/><br/>In the meantime, I am fascinated by these absolutely wonderful artistic interpretations:<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846615i/27220756._SX540_.jpg' width='' height='' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846615i/27220757._SX540_.jpg' width='' height='' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846708i/27220760._SX540_.jpg' width='' height='' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>(More to be found here: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.scoopwhoop.com/inothernews/mahabharata-reimagined-techno/#.0v0wnbvdj'>https://www.scoopwhoop.com/inothernew...</a> )</span>
  <span id="freeText9050264561852057049" style="display:none">One of the greatest epics of human civilisation, and a masterpiece of myth and legend. <br><br>As a result of its almost absurd scope and sheer length, I must admit to have merely skimmed this work (twice), but I aim to fully read it one day.<br><br>In the meantime, I am fascinated by these absolutely wonderful artistic interpretations:<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846615i/27220756._SX540_.jpg" width="" height="" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846615i/27220757._SX540_.jpg" width="" height="" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1552846708i/27220760._SX540_.jpg" width="" height="" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>(More to be found here: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.scoopwhoop.com/inothernews/mahabharata-reimagined-techno/#.0v0wnbvdj">https://www.scoopwhoop.com/inothernew...</a> )</span>
