<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8802277371451123433">Books can be attributed to &quot;Anonymous&quot; for several reasons: <br/><br/>* They are officially published under that name <br/>* They are traditional stories not attributed to a specific author <br/>* They are religious texts not generally attributed to a specific author <br/><br/>Books whose authorship is merely uncertain should be attributed to <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4699102.Unknown' title='Unknown' rel='nofollow noopener'>Unknown</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText8802277371451123433" style="display:none">Books can be attributed to "Anonymous" for several reasons: <br /><br />* They are officially published under that name <br />* They are traditional stories not attributed to a specific author <br />* They are religious texts not generally attributed to a specific author <br /><br />Books whose authorship is merely uncertain should be attributed to <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4699102.Unknown" title="Unknown" rel="nofollow noopener">Unknown</a>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8802277371451123433" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

